    "description": {
      "value": "<p>With this technique the user draws energy from the souls he previously absorbed and uses it to attack an objective. The energy takes the form of a ghostly skull and strikes the objective without a chance of missing its target. When the energy hits said target, it explodes dealing 4d10 points of damage to everything in a 20 ft. radius, half of it being sonic and half force damage. Other creatures caught in the area of effect must make a Reflex save for half damage. The target must be a human being.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Expendable Component:</b> Expendable Component -2 Soul Units.</p>\n",
